section_text: Cage of Death IVPromotionCombat Zone Wrestling [ 5 ] DateDecember 13 , 2002CityPhiladelphia , Pennsylvania [ 5 ] VenueECW Arena [ 5 ] Cage of Death IV took place on December 13 , 2002 , in Philadelphia , Pennsylvania at the Viking Hall and saw John Zandig defeat Lobo in a Cage of Death match for the ownership of CZW . This was the last Cage Of Death to use electricity as a hazard ( Lobo was electrocuted early in the match ) . [ 5 ]
